---
// Hero. Identity strip, plain headline, factual subhead naming the
// actual work. No italicized keyword. No em dashes. The pill links
// to /contact and signals availability without sounding like a job
// hunt.
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
  <div class="container-site hero__inner">
    <div class="hero__id animate-fade-up">
      <span class="hero__id-name">Moe Qadan</span>
      <span class="hero__id-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span class="hero__id-role">Senior UX &amp; frontend</span>
      <span class="hero__id-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span class="hero__id-loc">Los Angeles</span>
      <a href="/contact" class="hero__id-status" aria-label="Open to hearing about projects, go to contact">
        <span class="hero__id-status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Open to projects
      </a>
    </div>

    <h1 class="hero__headline animate-fade-up animate-delay-100">
      I do UX and frontend as one job.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero__paragraph animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">
      Design systems, content architecture, SEO, performance,
      accessibility, and AI-assisted prototyping all live in the same
      practice for me. Most days that means writing the components,
      maintaining the tokens, fixing the long tail of accessibility
      and perf regressions nobody is tracking, and shipping the next
      iteration before the standup is over.
    </p>

    <p class="hero__paragraph hero__paragraph--meta animate-fade-up animate-delay-300">
      Currently leading web experience at MagTek (a long-running
      ASP.NET MVC platform with a Razor partial library now past 100
      shared, typed components). Solo build alongside it:
      <a href="/work/chatobd2" class="hero__inline-link">ChatOBD2</a>,
      an AI-native diagnostics product. Earlier: 50+ wealth and
      banking portal deploys at InvestCloud, including Chase, Cetera,
      and Northwestern Mutual.
    </p>

    <div class="hero__ctas animate-fade-up animate-delay-400">
      <a
        href="/work"
        class="hero__cta hero__cta--primary"
        data-track="cta_click"
        data-track-cta="see-the-work"
        data-track-loc="home-hero"
      >
        See the work
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/approach"
        class="hero__cta hero__cta--ghost"
        data-track="cta_click"
        data-track-cta="approach"
        data-track-loc="home-hero"
      >How I work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: calc(60px + var(--space-10));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-12));
      padding-bottom: var(--space-20);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-16));
      padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + 96px);
      padding-bottom: 128px;
    }
  }

  .hero__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .hero__id {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px 10px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__id {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }

  .hero__id-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .hero__id-sep {
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero__id-role,
  .hero__id-loc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .hero__id-status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 3px 10px 3px 9px;
    margin-left: 4px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-success);
    background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 8%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 28%, transparent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 150ms, border-color 150ms;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero__id-status:hover {
    background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 14%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 50%, transparent);
  }

  .hero__id-status-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-success);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 65%, transparent);
    animation: hero-status-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes hero-status-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.85); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero__id-status-dot { animation: none; }
  }

  .hero__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(38px, 8.5vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.04;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 18ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__headline {
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.018em;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  .hero__paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .hero__paragraph--meta {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 16px);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hero__inline-link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    transition: color 150ms, text-decoration-color 150ms;
  }

  .hero__inline-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .hero__ctas {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px 12px;
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__ctas {
      margin-top: var(--space-10);
      gap: 12px 16px;
    }
  }

  .hero__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 0 22px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 200ms var(--ease-out), background-color 200ms, border-color 200ms, color 200ms, box-shadow 200ms;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero__cta--primary {
    background-color: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-text);
  }

  .hero__cta--primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
  }

  .hero__cta--ghost {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero__cta--ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .hero__ctas {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .hero__cta {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
